TY  - JOUR
TI  - Utility Theory without the Completeness Axiom
AU  - Aumann, Robert J.
AB  - [A utility theory is developed that parallels the von Neumann-Morgenstern utility theory, but makes no use of the assumption that preferences are complete (i.e., that any two alternatives are comparable).]
